      "filePath": "iac/provider-aws/modules/network/main.tf",
      "lineRange": [134, 147],
      "summary": "条件创建的 EC2 Instance Connect 端点,为私有子网中的 EC2 实例提供 SSH 访问能力,通过 connect_endpoint 安全组控制访问。",
      "tags": ["aws", "instance-connect", "ssh", "vpc-endpoint"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "resource:iac/provider-aws/modules/network/main.tf:aws_security_group.connect_endpoint",
      "type": "resource",
      "name": "aws_security_group.connect_endpoint",
      "filePath": "iac/provider-aws/modules/network/main.tf",
      "lineRange": [150, 170],
      "summary": "为 Instance Connect 端点创建的安全组,仅在 use_instance_connect 为 true 时创建,允许 22/tcp 出站至 VPC CIDR。",
      "tags": ["aws", "security-group", "instance-connect", "conditional"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
